{"tid":2036271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要搞黃色旅遊app！！動員外國人參與黃色經濟圈！！","createTime":"2020-05-26T11:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T20:52:29.000Z","uid":115965,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"aae8d3809041eca13ab0b83fb5eb9bec9025c56a","tid":2036271,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】旅遊業界提倡政府研究「旅遊氣泡」（Travel Bubble），旅發局總幹事程鼎一建議港府與亞洲地區，包括韓國、泰國、台灣、內地等商討，在雙方疫情受控等條件下，開放互相旅遊。有專家建議若開放旅遊，要抽旅客樣本驗病毒，以防無病徵患者進入本港。<br />\n<br />\n唔知國安法之後香港會變成點，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃色經濟圈要擴大去黃色旅遊業</span></span></span></span>！！而且要<span style=\"color: red;\">騎劫旅發局</span>依個乜鳩旅遊氣泡，趁佢開始向外搞宣傳個陣我地同時出動！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依幾日係twitter見到好多外國人（中、台、東南亞、西方都有）話唔知可以做乜先幫到香港，我地要比啲外國人知道佢地黎香港飲飲食食都可以幫到我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係twitter上面輕輕提過，即刻有內地人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAunZuP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAunZuP.png&h=5d386faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊brainstorm下可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚引玉：<br />\n<br />\n-黃色旅遊app，更加方便佢地搵路，而且可以有不同語言版本<br />\n<br />\n-儲印仔+打卡換紀念品，雖然可能又有大台爭議，但對旅客黎講係幾吸引，紀念品當係文宣黎啦 e.g印左文宣嘅口罩套<br />\n<br />\n-除左推餐廳，一定要推介其他黃店做買手信嘅地方！e.g文創店、糕餅店<br />\n<br />\n-推埋睇香港電影！！可以入戲院睇，民間亦可以搞抗爭題材嘅放映會<br />\n<br />\n其實可以連埋地區經濟搞，搞<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地區旅遊路線</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以天水圍為例<br />\n冇乜人知有個價值1700萬嘅單車公園，又有條7公里嘅單車徑，一路踩有唔少景點，踩埋去濕地公園都得，仲可以同locobike合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踩完去元朗食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人不才，只係有個咁嘅idea，希望有能之士見到可以把握時間實行，趁依家香港引起左國際關注同好多人嘅同情心，一定要比機會佢地參與先可以持續個attention。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家有計出計，路過都幫手推一推，希望比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你pay,和你eat嘅開發者/區議員</span></span>睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252f2db2a8925254c634916a23d85a015831bde1","tid":2036271,"uid":266011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"yellow trip advisor"},{"pid":"41ce7be4902d868525c7000ffc973c9361c6a179","tid":2036271,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"正wo"},{"pid":"7b8c847333e0eaed66a7ec4119ba683667dc5c93","tid":2036271,"uid":294003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"good idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推唔到都推下"},{"pid":"824d6e40f0355050276e5e28b69508d6171b2518","tid":2036271,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"push push push"},{"pid":"ea1c59255fc22dc499a76a5fa78e5f4ada0a631d","tid":2036271,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b205fd44e83422256e034ca8e049b6d11d3830","tid":2036271,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202